Lentil Burger

45 min
$5.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dietary Tags:

Cuisine:

Description

A hearty lentil burger that's packed with protein and flavor, perfect for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • cooked lentils: 1 cup
  • bread crumbs: 1/2 cup
  • shredded carrots: 1/2 cup
  • chopped onion: 1/4 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • egg: 1
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce leaves: 2
  • tomato slices: 1
  • cheese slices (optional): 2
